{"tid":1439842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英外相籲進行反修例風波全面獨立調查","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:08:10.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18bd50089272adcfda0a20350a2c89a4238bf21c","tid":1439842,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rr3wM7mh8-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRr3wM7mh8-E&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ca352390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rr3wM7mh8-E</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/UK-HK-190810-0915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FUK-HK-190810-0915.jpg&h=2fbdea9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】英國外相藍韜文與行政長官林鄭月娥通電話，呼籲對方就香港近期連串反修例示威進行全面獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部發表聲明指，藍韜文周五致電林鄭月娥，對香港的形勢和示威表示關注，強調英國支持《中英聯合聲明》中，列明香港實行高度自治以及對一國兩制的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文又譴責香港各方的暴力行為，但強調和平示威的權利，指香港有數以十萬計的市民選擇以和平示威表達意見，認為暴力事件不應蓋過大多數人的合法行動。他強調香港需要進行有意義的政治對話，以及進行全面獨立調查，以建立信任。"},{"pid":"bd9be3402e57a2ad63017733cf0ce1d430489b76","tid":1439842,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:49:05.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"382c10de0bb9ea66e3c7ae3393163f5386317712","tid":1439842,"uid":269965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}